User-profile-service
This service manages employees & authentication. It now supports JWT-based login/signup.

## 1. Backend Project Folder Structure 

user-service/
├── src/
│   └── main/
│       ├── java/
│       │   └── com/cloud/userservice/
│       │       ├── config/
│       │       │   ├── WebConfig.java
│       │       │   └── SecurityConfig.java
│       │       ├── controller/
